Package: vegawidget
Version: 0.0.2
Title: Htmlwidget Renderer for Vega and Vega-Lite
Description: Vega and Vega-Lite parse text in JSON notation to render 
  chart-specifications into HTML. This package is used to facilitate the 
  rendering.
